title: Watch Indian rocket launch record-breaking BlueBird 6 smartphone satellite to orbit tonight
description: An Indian LVM3 rocket is scheduled to launch the massive BlueBird 6 smartphone satellite for AST SpaceMobile tonight (Dec. 23), and you can watch the action live.
